![188.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1627483709282-6NCG7Z12VXR4IDPRA051/188.jpg)

POW! BAM! ZIP! 55 years ago the team known affectionately as the Dynamic Duo made their full-length feature film debut in Batman The Movie (1966). With Adam West as the Caped Crusader Batman and Burt Ward as The Boy Wonder Robin, we ushered in an entirely new era of Batmania! Join us on this 55th Anniversary as we look back at a "brighter" Batman and debate where he stands in the Batman Lexicon!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
